//
// test/sema/width/conditional_expr.test — conditional-expression
// width fixture (T024 rollover; specs/006-m3-sema/tasks.md Phase
// 4a). Per S14 + N1, `if (c) a else b` is the expression form;
// width is the LUB of the two branches. Asserts the
// `ConditionalExpr` carries a `: BitVector(N)` Type suffix per
// `emit-ast-format.contract.md` Invariant 2.

// RUN: printf 'module m {\n  wire c;\n  wire a;\n  wire b;\n  reg q = if (c) a else b;\n}\n' > %t.nsl
// RUN: %nslc -emit=ast %t.nsl | FileCheck %s

// CHECK: (RegDecl {{.*}}name=q
// CHECK: (ConditionalExpr {{.*}} : BitVector({{[0-9]+}})
